# 🏢 DEPARTMENT PAGES & TEAM CONTRIBUTORS
# =============================================================================
#
# ⚠️  REVIEW WORKFLOW & GOVERNANCE POLICY
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Department leads are the primary owners and are responsible for the first
# review of all changes within their domain.
#
# All merges additionally require a final review for overarching company
# standards, security, and governance. This is enforced via branch protection
# rules and is not configured here in CODEOWNERS.
#
# Standard Process:
# 1. Team Lead: Reviews & approves for domain quality and readiness.
# 2. Final Review: Automated check for compliance and standards.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

